Version 1.0 - released 2014-09-30
* updated to latest browser detection script (2014-08-01)

Version 1.0rc2 - released 2014-07-11
* fixed bug, where page specific templates overwrote handheld templates
  (solution works only for CMSimple_XH 1.6+) (reported by samecity)
* added plugin stylesheet
* added support for integrated plugin menu
* added metaconfig.php
* revised manuals
* improved QA

Version 1rc1 - released 2013-09-14
* updated to latest browser detection script (from 2013-09-03)
* added version.nfo
* added Czech localization and CTIMNE (contributed by oldnema)
* reviewed and updated manuals and README files
* refactored source code
* added Phing build.xml

Version 1beta5 - released 2012-10-19
* updated to new mobile detection from 2012-10-18
* fixed relocation to work with HTTPS and non default port numbers
* updated English manual
* added German manual
* added German translation
* added Slovak and Russian Translation (contributed by Tata resp. Old)

Version 1beta4 - released 2012-07-04
* changed: detection and redirection is done with PHP instead of JS
* added two alternative modes: redirect to sub-site, switch template instead of redirection
* added README, LICENSE and CHANGELOG
* added system check
* added manual

Version 1beta3 - 2011-09-02
* fixed bug: inclusion of jQuery4CMSimple didn't work in all circumstances

Version 1beta2 - released 2011-08-22
* initial release
